Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124771,126898}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129359,131653}No, you mustn't be holding that jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131861,136658}Evil spirits are in it! The moon's\Nevil spirits are locked in that jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136908,138993}The moon's evil spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139202,142372}You've got to come up with\Na better story than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:25.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142622,145875}It's true! If you hold it up\Nto the full moon…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146084,148211}…the evil spirits will\Nbe resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:33.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148628,153174}Stop your babbling!\NThis moon's jewel belongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:49.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164477,169148}STEAL THE JEWEL OF THE MOON!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:00.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176989,180451}– Meimi!\N– Oh, Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:04.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180910,184080}Hi. Talk about great timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184330,188668}I'm on my way to cover a story.\NDo you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:14.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189377,194882}Why should I go with you, when I'm\Nnot even on the news-writing staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195133,198845}Because you understand\Nmy intellectual reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:24.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200096,204517}– I wouldn't say that, exactly.\N– Anyway, we're wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204726,208771}Hey, wait a minute.\NSawatari, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:33.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209147,213693}That Sawatari! Where does he think\Nhe's taking Meimi to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223327,225955}May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:52.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226205,232044}I came because I wanted to pray,\Nbut I don't know how to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232420,235840}My name's Mochida.\NThis is rather embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:04:01.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236090,241053}I used to be a burglar.\NI just got out of prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241596,243431}A burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:08.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243681,248478}Please don't get me wrong.\NI'm trying to go straight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:14.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250688,254233}Only thing is, I have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254692,257695}Perhaps it would help\Nif you talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257945,260656}All the things\NI stole were returned…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:27.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260907,267038}…to their rightful owners\Nby the police while I was in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:32.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267622,272376}All except one. A jewel which\Ncontains the moon's evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273002,274587}The moon's evil spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:40.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274837,280551}Right after I stole the jewel,\Nits owner died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:47.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281177,287141}He had no family,\Nand the jewel was forgotten about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:54.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289018,294398}After that, it slipped past the police\Nand was sold several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:05:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294649,300530}I finally located the present owner\Nand asked him to return the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:06.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301155,306244}What did you intend to do with\Nthe jewel when you got it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306494,309038}I want to return it\Nto its rightful owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:12.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309247,312917}I mean, I want to leave it\Nat his gravesite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313167,314919}That's very honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315378,319507}That's the only thing\NI can do in atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:24.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319757,324637}But the present owner turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:29.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325388,329600}I thought about stealing\Nthe jewel back, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:34.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329851,334355}No, you mustn't steal, not after\Nyou worked so hard to reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:38.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334605,338860}You're right.\NStealing it just wouldn't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:43.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339068,343614}Why don't you pray again and this\Ntime put your entire heart in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:47.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343865,347785}Yes, I'll do that.\NThank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348035,350538}By the way, where is that jewel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:55.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351122,355751}It's called the Jewel of the Moon\Nand is on display at the Space Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:00.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356168,360715}Oh, yes, I've heard it's supposed\Nto glow like the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361757,364677}So this is the Jewel of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367138,368764}It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:13.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369015,373603}There's a rumor that the evil spirits\Nof the moon are trapped in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373853,375646}That's just hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:20.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376063,380568}I wonder. Still, it is exciting\Nto think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387366,389327}That's the space stage…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389577,393831}…made to simulate\Nthe weightlessness in outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396000,398502}That planet looks like the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:43.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399045,403883}That's a holograph,\Na 3-D picture of the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404133,407261}Rats, I forgot to take pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407929,412725}Meimi, get closer to\Nthe Jewel of the Moon. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:58.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413142,418230}Yes, two beautiful objects.\NThis will make a nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419941,423527}Wait a minute, don't bother me.\NI'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:08.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424403,428866}Like I said— Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429825,432787}Didn't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434205,436582}Never mind that. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436832,438334}Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:24.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439418,444298}I'll bet you followed us here because\Nyou got jealous seeing us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444548,447218}Why would I be jealous\Nabout a girl like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447468,449971}Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450221,453599}All right then, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:38.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454475,458270}I came here to see how\Ntheir security system is set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458813,460648}The security system?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460856,462692}Please, Mr. Urano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:47.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463317,467947}Please, Mr. Urano. Give the Jewel\Nof the Moon back to me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468197,470366}You must be out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470616,473911}I'd be a fool to give it\Nto a former thief like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474245,477915}Why can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:02.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478165,482461}– Enough of this! Throw him out.\N– Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:07.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482712,487591}Let me go!\NMr. Urano, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:13.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488843,493764}I went through the black market and\Npaid a lot of money to get that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494015,496976}I'm not letting that thief\Nget his hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497184,500021}I'm going to get rich\Nputting it on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500271,502481}The trouble with you is…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513367,515619}Are you all right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:39.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515870,519206}Thank you. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526589,530593}I see. So that's what his motive was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:55.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531135,535097}The way things are, Mr. Mochida\Nwill resort to stealing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535347,538851}Let's get that jewel back for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539602,541812}Yes, Seira, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:13.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547943,553491}Boy, that Sawatari sure\Nhas a big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553741,555242}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555993,558621}"I'm going to\Nthe Space Museum tonight…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558871,561707}…to steal the Jewel of the Moon.\N– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562541,565544}What's going on? Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:35.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572051,575638}I wish she'd give me\Nnotice ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580184,583062}Stupid Asuka Jr.\NHe's always interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:50.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587274,590694}Hey, Asuka Jr., what's the big rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:55.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590945,595157}Get out of my way!\NI can't be wasting time with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599120,600996}It's from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:05.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601205,605000}This is the break I've been\Nwaiting for! Asuka Jr., wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:13.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609004,613425}Sorry, Ruby. I have a job to do.\NI'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:22.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618305,622184}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627064,628941}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630568,632528}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633737,636824}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:55.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649920,655759}Still, it does bother me to think\Nthere's evil in that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:00.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656510,660472}Oh, Seira, that's nothing but hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:06.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660931,666145}Yes, but you mustn't let your guard\Ndown. Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666729,669356}Don't worry. I'll handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:15.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671734,675321}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676989,679408}I don't need your services.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680326,682411}Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:29.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682620,689084}Even if you don't hire me, the mayor\Nhas ordered me to arrest St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691879,693339}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695925,699511}Wow, look at all the equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:45.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700137,705434}With equipment like this, St. Tail is\Nno more than a mouse, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:50.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705893,710648}Mr. Urano, this equipment is\Nno match for St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711065,714735}Well, if you're going to insist,\Ndo as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:58.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714985,718364}Just don't interfere with our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:04.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719615,724245}– Yes, I understand.\N– Boy, what a grouch!
Comment: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:05.74,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:725746,725746}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:10.75,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:730751,730751}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750729,754650}It's been forced open, but by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:46.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761282,766787}Boy, I'm getting old.\NI'm already out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784805,788434}– What's wrong?\N– I thought I saw a shadow on monitor A.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788684,791228}– You what?\N– Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:22.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799611,802156}Why, that's Mr. Mochida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:28.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802990,808370}I can't let him commit a crime.\NI've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:39.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815419,819048}– It must have been my imagination.\N– Don't fall apart on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820924,822551}It's St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823677,825554}Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:52.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826513,832269}Even the infamous St. Tail couldn't\Nsteal the jewel from this museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843906,845199}Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856251,858379}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860839,862841}Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:27.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864051,867179}Rats! You're not\Ngetting away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874269,876188}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:41.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878273,881318}It's a high electrical current!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889284,891203}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892204,893997}Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898127,900671}Come back here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910097,912975}Snap out of it, Mr. Mochida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:19.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915894,919565}Mr. Urano, using high voltage\Nis very dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:25.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920524,925362}I will use every means available\Nto protect my priceless display.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925863,930909}You didn't tell us you hid the jewel\Nand were displaying a holograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931160,932369}That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:36.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932619,936540}I'm not so stupid that I'd let\Nsomeone steal my jewel so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936790,939376}It sent St. Tail—\NI mean, Holy Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:43.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939626,943630}…scampering away with her tail\Nbetween her legs. How fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:55.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949386,955142}Damn that Urano.\NHe hid the Jewel of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:16:00.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955392,960105}Mr. Mochida, I promise I'll get\Nthe Jewel of the Moon back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966695,972701}I can't do my job unless\Nyou tell me where the real jewel is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:19.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972951,979249}Your services are not needed. We can\Ntake care of St. Tail ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:25.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979500,985964}Let's go. St. Tail took quite a blow.\NI don't think she'll be back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:31.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986215,991345}No, I'm sure she'll return.\NIt's in her nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993555,997059}That's strange.\NMonitor F has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999561,1003524}What's going on?\NThe hologram system's being activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:47.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004024,1007528}All the monitors are showing\Nthe hologram system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007778,1009488}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009738,1011198}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013742,1016995}I've got it.\NI know where the jewel's hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017246,1019498}What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:14.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029841,1034263}Mr. Urano,\Nthat moon is the jewel, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:21.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037140,1041687}Oh, I get it. He hid it\Ninside the holograph image!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044606,1045691}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:29.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046358,1049361}St. Tail, I'll get you\Nfor sure tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:35.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050946,1055659}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:43.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057327,1063458}I'm inviting you three\Nto the space station!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080642,1083437}– Rats!\N– This is some scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:12.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087858,1092613}If I turn the power off,\Nthe anti-gravity field will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092821,1095782}St. Tail, you'll be thrown\Nto the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109671,1111381}Why doesn't she fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113133,1115636}The jewel is mine.\NI'm not giving it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125937,1128231}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131276,1133028}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137908,1139993}This couldn't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142829,1144956}It's the evil from the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145207,1147626}No! The jewel is acting as a lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147876,1152631}The moonlight hit it and it's\Ngiving off that blinding glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160180,1161682}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164685,1167938}I'm taking the Jewel of the Moon\Nback with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168188,1169856}St. Tail, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172192,1174486}Rats! She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:40.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174736,1180409}Don't get depressed. I have a picture\Nof her right here in my camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190293,1194423}I am returning your jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195006,1197759}May you rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:06.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200679,1206977}St. Tail, with your help,\NI managed to stay clean. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:23.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219197,1223869}We're finally going\Nto uncover St. Tail's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228373,1231793}– What's this?\N– I don't remember taking this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:36.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232002,1236757}You lousy reporter, all that talk\Nabout unveiling St. Tail's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237007,1239134}Shut up, you miserable detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239384,1241553}– Why, you!\N– The same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243221,1245932}If you're so hot,\Nwhy don't you arrest St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246183,1248059}Why, you!
